description: Migom Global Corp., through its subsidiaries, engages in retail banking and money service business worldwide. The company offers lending, leasing, investment, and money transmittal services; credit and debit cards, travelers cheques, bankers drafts, and electronic banking services; and guarantees and commitment, credit reference, custody of securities, foreign exchange and precious metal dealing, investment banking, and corporate finance services, as well as electronic money and payment services. The company was formerly known as Alfacourse Inc. and changed its name to Migom Global Corp. in November 2019. Migom Global Corp. was incorporated in 2016 and is based in New York, New York. Migom Global Corp. is a subsidiary of Heritage Equity Fund LP.
